ed="T" n="0820b10"/><persName key="A012060">釋檀特師</persName>者，一名<persName key="A012060">慧豐</persName>，不知何許人也。身<lb
ed="T" n="0820b11"/>雖剃染<ptr type="glossary" target="#g30"/>，率略無檢制，飲酒啖肉，語默無常。<lb
ed="T" n="0820b12"/>逆<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1229"/>論來事，後必如言。居于<placeName key="PL000000045061">武威</placeName>，肆意狂逸。<lb
ed="T" n="0820b13"/>時<persName key="A012061">宇文仲和</persName>為<anchor xml:id="beg0820002"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0820002"/>史，請<ref type="person" target="#A012060">之</ref>入<ref type="place" target="#PL000000045052">州</ref>，歷觀厩<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1234"/><lb
ed="T" n="0820b14"/>庫，乃云：「何意畜他官物邪？」<persName key="A012061">仲和</persName>不諭其旨，<lb
ed="T" n="0820b15"/>怒之，不令在城。未幾，<persName key="A012061">仲和</persName>拒不受代，朝<lb
ed="T" n="0820b16"/>延令<persName key="A012062">獨孤信</persName>擒之<ptr target="#n2300"/>。<persName key="A012061">仲和</persName>身死，資財沒官。<persName key="A002055">周<lb
ed="T" n="0820b17"/>文</persName>聞之，降書召之。<persName key="A012060">檀特</persName>至<placeName key="PL000000042853"><anchor xml:id="beg0820sgsz14"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0820sgsz14"/>州</placeName>，會<persName key="A005264">齊神武</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0820b18"/>來寇<placeName key="PL000000005016">玉壁</placeName>，<persName key="A012060">檀特</persName>曰：「狗豈能到<placeName key="PL000000005238">龍門</placeName>邪？」<persName key="A005264">神武</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0820b19"/>果不至<placeName key="PL000000005238">龍門</placeName>而還<ptr target="#n2301"/>。<persName key="A004282">侯景</persName>未叛<placeName key="PL000000058418">東魏</placeName>之前，忽<lb
ed="T" n="0820b20"/>捉一杖，杖頭刻為獼猴形，令其面常向西，<lb
ed="T" n="0820b21"/>日夜弄旃<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1050"/>。又索一角弓牽挽之。俄而<persName key="A004282">侯景</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0820b22"/>啟降，尋復背叛歸<placeName key="PL000000027711">梁</placeName>，皆可徵驗。至<date from-iso="+0551-01-25" key="j19223331922420" to-iso="+0551-04-22"><name>大統</name>十<lb
ed="T" n="0820b23"/>七年春</date>初，忽著一布帽。<persName key="A002055">周文</persName>左右驚問之，<lb
ed="T" n="0820b24"/><persName key="A012060">檀特</persName>曰：「汝亦著，<ref type="person" target="#A002055">王</ref>亦著也。」至<date from-iso="+0551-03-25" key="j19223921922420" to-iso="+0551-04-22">三月</date>而<persName key="A002048">魏文帝</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0820b25"/>崩。復取一白絹帽戴之，左右復問之。<persName key="A012060">檀特</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0820b26"/>曰：「汝亦著，<ref type="person" target="#A002055">王</ref>亦著也。」未畿<ref type="person" target="#A019426">丞相夫人</ref>薨。後復<lb
ed="T" n="0820b27"/>戴，問對同前<ptr target="#n2302"/>，尋<ref type="person" target="#A002055">丞相</ref>第二子<persName key="A019427">武邑公</persName>薨。其事<lb
ed="T" n="0820b28"/>驗多如此也。俄而病卒，<persName key="A002055">周文</persName>命葬之。</p>
